column1: Survey Title: Student's Satisfaction and Perception Towards Online Shopping

column4: How often do you buy on Online Shops (eCommerce sites)?
column5: Which E-commerce Site/Platform do you use the most?
column6: How much in total do you spend on Online Shopping Monthly?
column7: What is your biggest concern in terms of buying Online?
column8: I am very happy and satisfied with my online shopping experience regardless of which platform.
column9: I have not experienced or less encountered problems on parcel deliveries.
column10: Online shopping is very convenient for me, and it helps with the current situation especially during this pandemic.
column11: I can save money because prices Online are much cheaper than in Physical Stores.
column12: I can easily manage my time because Online shopping has made it easier for me to buy things I need.
column13: I plan to continue buying goods and items online.
